title: Fifteen (Taylor's Version)
description:
So many emotions tied to the song Fifteen, and it brings back A LOT of memories! What was Taylor's true meaning behind the song that immediately became the high school anthem? And what differences can we hear in Taylor's version?
Lacey, Amy, Nick and Ana discuss and dissect this song!
Chime in with us! What did we miss? What are you looking forward to hearing?
